  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Yantai North Andre Juice Co., Ltd. (North Andre or the company) is one of Chinas leading producers and exporters of apple juice concentrate (AJC).  Established in 1996, North Andre has become a major global AJC participant with total processing capacity in excess of 150,000 tons per season.  Its net sales rose about 55% in 2003 to $44.0 million and based on year-to-day figures continue to grow robustly in 2004.  North Andre is listed on the Growth Enterprise Market of the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong.

North Andre has been pursuing an expansion and diversification business strategy within the apple juice and related-products sector.  It upgraded and/or expanded plants in the following provinces:  Shannxi, Shandong (two plants), and Jiangsu.</narrative>
  </description>
