    <narrative xml:lang="EN">Headquartered in Yantai city, Shandong province, North Andre now has four wholly owned operating plants all within proximity to major apple production regions.  The four plant locations are:

-  Muping district of Yantai city, Shandong province;
-  Baishui county of western Shannxi province;
-  Longkou county of Shandong province; and 
